name: "Creepy Joe (Wild Life)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Crayon and sticker collage on cardstock with digital embellishments, color, and moshing.] Oh Creepy Joe, you complete bastard. Rumor has it has was eventually poisoned by a jilted lover, although his body was never found. What ACTUALLY happened (says the omniscient narrator) is that he was eventually hauled, bodily, into HELL...by a jilted lover... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
